What Is OP151XGS?

OP151XGS is a 10G XGS-PON ONU SFP+ module designed for direct fiber connectivity through standard SFP+ interfaces.

Instead of using traditional external ISP ONT devices, the module installs directly into routers, switches or firewall appliances, enabling:

cleaner deployment architecture
lower power consumption
reduced cabling complexity
native 10G fiber access
enterprise-grade networking workflows
