Why Use ONU SFP+ Modules?

Traditional ISP ONT deployments typically require:

Fiber → ONT → Ethernet → Router

ONU SFP+ modules simplify the architecture:

Fiber → ONU SFP+ → Router

This reduces:

external hardware
power adapters
Ethernet cabling
rack complexity
deployment overhead
