Frequently Asked Questions
Can OP151XGS replace ISP ONT devices?

Yes. OP151XGS is designed for direct XGS-PON integration and can replace traditional ONT hardware in compatible environments.

Does OP151XGS support MikroTik routers?

Yes. The module is commonly used with MikroTik CCR routers and RouterOS 7 deployments.

Does the module support 10G XGS-PON?

Yes. OP151XGS supports native 10G XGS-PON connectivity.

Is 8311 firmware supported?

Yes. OP151XGS supports 8311 firmware and advanced management workflows.

Can ONU SFP+ modules simplify fiber deployments?

Yes. ONU SFP+ modules reduce hardware complexity and provide direct integration into networking equipment.

